# Verdigris Nation Ledger  
**Sovereign Trust Infrastructure of the Verdigris Botanica Tribal Nation Trust**

---

### Mission

This repository serves as the **official public ledger** and **digital archive** of trust declarations, contracts, compliance certifications, audit logs, and sovereign financial data under the jurisdiction of the **Verdigris Botanica Tribal Nation Trust**.

All records are constitutional, sacred, and legally binding.

---

### Ledger Contents

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `DECLARATION OF FEDERAL RECOGNITION AND HIGH OFFIC.docx` | Foundational declaration of status |
| `Verdigris_KYC_Compliance_Packet.pdf` | Sovereign identity and entity verification |
| `postal contract.pdf` | Postal sovereignty & operations contract |
| `Audit Log.csv` | Transactional ledger of node activity |
| `verdigrisbotanicanation.gov.txt` | `.gov` domain validation file |
| Additional images & PDFs | Seals, documents, record scans |

